@startuml BABIFIX - Sequence Chat Temps Reel
!theme plain

skinparam backgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam sequenceStyle uml2

skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #90CAF9
  BorderColor #1976D2
}

skinparam entity {
  BackgroundColor #C8E6C9
  BorderColor #2E7D32
}

skinparam boundary {
  BackgroundColor #FFE082
  BorderColor #FF8F00
}

skinparam control {
  BackgroundColor #E1BEE7
  BorderColor #7B1FA2
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color #64B5F6
}

title **BABIFIX** - Sequence Chat & Notifications Temps Reel\nArchitecure Hybride: REST + WebSocket + FCM

actor "Client" as Client
actor "Prestataire" as Prestataire
participant "BABIFIX App\n(Flutter)" as AppClient
participant "BABIFIX Pro\n(Flutter)" as AppPro
participant "ClientEventsConsumer" as ClientWS
participant "PrestataireEventsConsumer" as ProWS
database "Redis\n(Channel Layer)" as Redis
participant "Django API\n(REST)" as API
participant "Firebase\n(FCM)" as FCM

== Connexion WebSocket (Evenements globaux) ==

Client -> AppClient : Ouverture application
activate AppClient
AppClient -> ClientWS : CONNECT\nwss://api.babifix.ci/ws/client-events/?token=JWT
activate ClientWS
ClientWS -> Redis : Join group\nbabifix_client_events
Redis --> ClientWS : Channel joined
ClientWS --> AppClient : WebSocket connected

Prestataire -> AppPro : Ouverture application
activate AppPro
AppPro -> ProWS : CONNECT\nwss://api.babifix.ci/ws/prestataire-{user_id}/?token=JWT
activate ProWS
ProWS -> Redis : Join group\nbabifix_prestataire_{user_id}
Redis --> ProWS : Channel joined
ProWS --> AppPro : WebSocket connected

deactivate ClientWS
deactivate ProWS

== Envoi de message (API REST) ==

Client -> AppClient : Tape message\n"Bonjour, je suis disponible a 14h"
AppClient -> AppClient : Input validation

AppClient -> API : POST /api/messages\n{conversation_id, body: "..."}
activate API
API -> API : Save to PostgreSQL
API --> AppClient : Message saved
deactivate API

' Broadcast via WebSocket pour les utilisateurs en ligne
API -> Redis : PUBLISH babifix_client_events\n{type: chat.message, ...}
API -> Redis : PUBLISH babifix_prestataire_{prestataire_id}\n{type: chat.message, ...}

' Notification FCM pour les utilisateurs hors ligne
API -> FCM : sendPushNotification(user_id, title: "Nouveau message", body: "...")
activate FCM
FCM --> AppPro : FCM Push (background/termine)
deactivate FCM

== Indicateur de frappe (WebSocket uniquement) ==

Client -> AppClient : Commence a taper
AppClient -> ClientWS : SEND\n{type: typing, conversation_id: ...}
ClientWS -> Redis : PUBLISH babifix_prestataire_{prestataire_id}
Redis -> ProWS : TYPING\n{is_typing: true}
ProWS -> AppPro : Show "Client tape..."

Client -> AppClient : Arrete de taper (3s timeout)
AppClient -> ClientWS : SEND\n{type: typing, is_typing: false}
ClientWS -> Redis : PUBLISH
Redis -> ProWS : TYPING\n{is_typing: false}
ProWS -> AppPro : Hide typing indicator

deactivate AppClient
deactivate AppPro

note right of ClientWS
  Django Channels
  - Consumer: ClientEventsConsumer
  - Group: babifix_client_events (global)
  - Redis Channel Layer
  Pas de Consumer par reservation
end note

note right of API
 messages transitent par API REST
  (POST /api/messages, GET /api/messages)
  Pas de WebSocket pour les messages eux-memes
end note

note right of ProWS
  Django Channels
  - Consumer: PrestataireEventsConsumer
  - Group: babifix_prestataire_{user_id} (par utilisateur)
  - Redis Channel Layer
  Notifications ciblees par utilisateur
end note

@enduml